Title: myHealth
Description: myHealth provides a innovative way to track your training progress by tagging images with various training information (Body Fat%, Weight, etc)
HomeWiki:
Welcome to myHealth


myHealth is a innovative way to track your training progress by tagging photos with training information (like body fat% and current weight)

For the developer:
myHealth was written using WPF. Some of the leassons I have learned while writting myHealth has been documented on my blog (http://dotnet.org.za/rudi/archive/2008/06/23/myhealth.aspx)
